Package ePortfolio

Class Investment

  • java.lang.Object
    • ePortfolio.Investment
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MutualFund, Stock
    public abstract class Investment
extends java.lang.Object
    An Investment object. Parent to Stock investment and MutualFund investment objects. Investment objects contains all attributes of any investment and unique functionalities that are inherited by its children allowing manipulation of the Portfolio.
